>然后等待这批小孩长大,中国就有自己的操作系统生态了.<br /><br />以上纯属瞎想,毕竟早些年武侠小说背了孩子读书成绩差的锅,现在是电子设备,家长们从来不会想到是自己的问题.<br />顺便能解决:浙江地区高考,考 python 笔试,脑算 photoshop,flash 的编辑器,甚至考特定版本的 bug", "last_modified": 1643688118, "replies": 40, "id": 831575}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 2876, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 761, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 395888, "username": "Zhouisme", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zhouisme", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/421b5744cbf11ff09b94a35b9d86ab16?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/421b5744cbf11ff09b94a35b9d86ab16?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/421b5744cbf11ff09b94a35b9d86ab16?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1553695979, "last_modified": 1553695979}, "last_reply_by": "EminemW", "last_touched": 1643667827, "title": "一个人在外地过年都吃了点什么？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/831528", "created": 1643621744, "deleted": 0, "content": "因公司项目原因老板要求有人*留守*，所不能回家过年，今年排到了我。毕业第二年无奈，准备累点工作经验跳槽回本地。\r\n\r\n晚饭一个在宿舍吃，准备了一条鱼进行清蒸，一个简单火锅，一些泥螺。\r\n\r\n不知跟我一样不在家一个人过年的你给自己准备了什么吃的？", "content_rendered": "<p>因公司项目原因老板要求有人<em>留守</em>，所不能回家过年，今年排到了我。毕业第二年无奈，准备累点工作经验跳槽回本地。</p>\n<p>晚饭一个在宿舍吃，准备了一条鱼进行清蒸，一个简单火锅，一些泥螺。</p>\n<p>不知跟我一样不在家一个人过年的你给自己准备了什么吃的？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1643621851, "replies": 31, "id": 831528}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1629391393", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1629391393",